data.description: Looking for a CUTE home with upgrades and curb appeal?  Take the time to look at the 3 bedroom, two bath home located on the North side of Abilene.  The open kitchen and dining room provide a great space for entertaining or for those holiday gatherings.  With recently painted kitchen, newly installed range, microwave, and vinyl flooring throughout, this home is ready for it's next owner.  In addition to all of this, there is a large back yard, covered patio area and two storage buildings.  Make sure to add this one to your list of must see homes in Abilene!
